{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/using-github-action-to-deploy-hexo-blog","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"56e32900-2cee-5083-83fd-bef3051b436a","html":"<p>Hexo 打完文章之後都樣手動下 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo g</code> 產生靜態頁面, 再透過 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo d</code> 來 deploy 到 github page上.</p>\n<p>這次希望可以透過 Github action 來簡化這些手動流程, 希望寫完文章就可以自動 deploy 上去.</p>\n<p>Github action 每個月可以免費用 2000 分鐘, 對這使用情境而言是綽綽有餘了.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/b1945/github_action_price.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/8ac56/github_action_price.webp 240w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/d3be9/github_action_price.webp 480w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/e46b2/github_action_price.webp 960w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/f992d/github_action_price.webp 1440w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/882b9/github_action_price.webp 1920w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/7f7f7/github_action_price.webp 2754w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/8ff5a/github_action_price.png 240w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/e85cb/github_action_price.png 480w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/d9199/github_action_price.png 960w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/07a9c/github_action_price.png 1440w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/29114/github_action_price.png 1920w,\n/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/b1945/github_action_price.png 2754w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/06022c4e45db4b0dfb4ede51c862b0f6/d9199/github_action_price.png\"\n            alt=\"github_action_price\"\n            title=\"github_action_price\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"hexo-架構\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hexo-%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B\" aria-label=\"hexo 架構 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>hexo 架構</h2>\n<p>目前我 repo 是由 <code class=\"language-text\">master</code> 來放靜態頁面, 直接透過 github page 來存取 blog</p>\n<p>而 <code class=\"language-text\">backup</code> branch 拿來放 hexo 的 source</p>\n<p>可以直接從我的 repo 看, <a href=\"https://github.com/owlran/owlran.github.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">我的repo</a></p>\n<p>所以我的 Github action 這邊等到 <code class=\"language-text\">backup</code> branch 有東西 push 才會去呼叫後面一連串的動作</p>\n<h2 id=\"權限\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%90\" aria-label=\"權限 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>權限</h2>\n<p>先透過 <code class=\"language-text\">ssh-keygen</code> 生成 public key, private key 後面兩個步驟會用到</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ssh-keygen -f deploy-key</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"settings--deploy-keys\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#settings--deploy-keys\" aria-label=\"settings  deploy keys permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Settings > Deploy keys</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>settings → Deploy keys → add deploy key</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>新增一個叫 <code class=\"language-text\">DEPLOY_KEY_PUB</code> 的 deploy key 內容從 <code class=\"language-text\">deploy-key.pub</code> 裡面複製貼上.</p>\n<h3 id=\"settings--secrets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#settings--secrets\" aria-label=\"settings  secrets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Settings > Secrets</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>settings → Secrets → add a new secret</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>新增一個叫 <code class=\"language-text\">DEPLOY_KEY</code> 的 secret 內容從 <code class=\"language-text\">deploy-key</code> 裡面複製貼上.</p>\n<h2 id=\"_configyml-要由-ssh-的方式來做-hexo-deploy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#_configyml-%E8%A6%81%E7%94%B1-ssh-%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BE%86%E5%81%9A-hexo-deploy\" aria-label=\"_configyml 要由 ssh 的方式來做 hexo deploy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>_config.yml 要由 ssh 的方式來做 hexo deploy</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># Deployment\n## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\ndeploy:\n  type: git\n  repository: git@github.com:owlran/owlran.github.io.git\n  branch: master</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"github-action\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#github-action\" aria-label=\"github action permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Github action</h2>\n<p>hexo 的 theme 是用 submodule 的方式來管理, 所以 <code class=\"language-text\">Update themes</code> 那步要記得做</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">name: CI\non:\n  push:\n    branches:\n      - backup \njobs:\n  build:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v1\n      - name: Use Node.js ${{ matrix.node_version }}\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v1\n        with:\n          node_version: ${{ matrix.node_version }}\n      - name: Configuration environment\n        env:\n          DEPLOY_KEY: ${{secrets.DEPLOY_KEY}}\n        run: |\n          mkdir -p ~/.ssh/\n          echo &quot;$DEPLOY_KEY&quot; | tr -d &#39;\\r&#39; &gt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa\n          echo &quot;$DEPLOY_KEY&quot;\n          chmod 600 ~/.ssh/id_rsa\n          ssh-keyscan github.com &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/known_hosts\n          git config --global user.name &quot;owlran&quot;\n          git config --global user.email &quot;owlran1088@gmail.com&quot;\n      - name: Update themes\n        run: |\n          git submodule init\n          git submodule update\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: |\n          npm i -g hexo-cli\n          npm i\n      - name: Generate hexo\n        run: |\n          hexo generate\n      - name: Deploy hexo\n        run: |\n          hexo deploy</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://op30132.github.io/2020/02/05/github-action/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hexo + github actions 自動化部署</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/using-github-action-to-deploy-hexo-blog","tagSlugs":["/tag/hexo/","/tag/github-action/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-04-26T22:40:32.169Z","description":"透過 Github action 來自動化 Hexo deploy 流程","tags":["Hexo","Github action"],"title":"用 Github action 自動 deploy hexo","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/6d93cbc4956a854d4c4369f0e281e7f3/42-line-bible.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/using-github-action-to-deploy-hexo-blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}